by ogizanagi at 2018-09-21T18:31:05Z

@javiereguiluz : You might still be on OS X Sierra, but this emoji is part of Unicode 10 for which the Apple Color Emoji font was only updated since High Sierra.

_Note: You can try installing the [emoji-one font](https://github.com/emojione/emojione/tree/master/extras/fonts#apple-font) or get a more recent version of the Apple font from another High Sierra install._

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

